reviewText: Sorry please update the bad review about not being able to see both movies on "one dvd".  As a suggestion the company should give clear instructions that the second video is on the flip side.  The problem is the video has no markings it looks like a "copy of a DVD" you would make yourself without placing any labeling on it.  The DVD quality is poor but the important fact is that you can see both videos as promised on the one "DVD".

reviewText: I am a fan of Sandra Bullock and there are very few things I don't love about her work. This grouping of movies by her are 4 of my favorites. I have nothing bad to say about them except if you have not seen a lot of her work these will introduce to her comic side. I would pay for them individually and finding them all together in a collecting is plain gold at a quarter of the cost. These movies are extremely good whether Miss Bullock is staring in them or not and the fact she is ... a major bonus!
